=== Dependencies:
gem install yammer4r

=== To get up and running

Basically you need to generate an oauth.yam file so you can run notifyammer.rb script.

1) Download script:
curl -O https://github.com/jpatterson/yammer4r/blob/master/bin/yammer_create_oauth_yml.rb

2) Create your yammer app
https://www.yammer.com/client_applications/new

3) Have with you consumer key and secret

4) Run yammer_create_oauth_yml.rb script, that will generate a oauth.yam file 

5) Now you are ready to play with notifyammer.rb
